2) Big City Adventure: London Classic



Genre: Hidden Object | Puzzle


Search for thousands of cleverly hidden items around the historic sites of 
jolly old London in Big City Adventure: London Classic! Collect postcards containing fascinating and obscure facts about London and its history and earn cool mementos from the amazing scenes you'll visit in this fun Hidden Object 
game. Play unique minigames and explore a beautiful city in Big City Adventure: London Classic!


Collect postcards
Find awesome mementos
Jolly Old London awaits!


System Requirements:


OS: Windows XP | Windows Vista | Windows 7
CPU: 800 MHz
